This Hospital Work and Lead Workflow Dashboard provides an overview of hospital operations, patient trends, and financial performance. 
It helps hospital management monitor admissions, diagnoses, doctor feedback, and billing insights.

1️⃣ Patient Timeline & Financial Summary
2️⃣ Bed Occupancy Analysis
3️⃣ Doctor Feedback Distribution
4️⃣ Diagnosis Types
5️⃣ Billing vs Health Insurance Analysis
6️⃣ Filters & Controls

The dashboard helps hospital administrators track patient flow, disease trends, bed utilization, doctor performance, and 
revenue vs insurance coverage, enabling better operational and financial decision-making.
